38#include "gmp.h"
39#include "gmp-impl.h"
40
41
42mp_limb_t
43mpn_dcpi1_div_q (mp_ptr qp, mp_ptr np, mp_size_t nn,
44 mp_srcptr dp, mp_size_t dn, gmp_pi1_t *dinv)
45{
46 mp_ptr tp, wp;
47 mp_limb_t qh;
48 mp_size_t qn;
49 TMP_DECL;
50
51 TMP_MARK;
52
53 ASSERT (dn >= 6);
54 ASSERT (nn - dn >= 3);
55 ASSERT (dp[dn-1] & GMP_NUMB_HIGHBIT);
56
57 tp = TMP_ALLOC_LIMBS (nn + 1);
58 MPN_COPY (tp + 1, np, nn);
59 tp[0] = 0;
60
61 qn = nn - dn;
62 wp = TMP_ALLOC_LIMBS (qn + 1);
63
64 qh = mpn_dcpi1_divappr_q (wp, tp, nn + 1, dp, dn, dinv);
65
66 if (wp[0] == 0)
67 {
68 mp_limb_t cy;
69
70 if (qn > dn)
71 mpn_mul (tp, wp + 1, qn, dp, dn);
72 else
73 mpn_mul (tp, dp, dn, wp + 1, qn);
74
75 cy = (qh != 0) ? mpn_add_n (tp + qn, tp + qn, dp, dn) : 0;
76
77 if (cy || mpn_cmp (tp, np, nn) > 0) /* At most is wrong by one, no cycle. */
78 qh -= mpn_sub_1 (qp, wp + 1, qn, 1);
79 else /* Same as below */
80 MPN_COPY (qp, wp + 1, qn);
81 }
82 else
83 MPN_COPY (qp, wp + 1, qn);
84
85 TMP_FREE;
86 return qh;
87}
